::{{DIcon|Talk}} You mentioned that you hugged Yanqing?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502140103-->
:::'''Hongling:''' Hehe, it's actually very simple. As the saying goes, "in the world of martial arts, speed is king." It's the same thing with chasing after your idol. All that matters is being fast enough.
:::'''Hongling:''' To raise my speed and strength, I trained so much in running and grappling techniques for a month that I even wore out several pairs of shoes.
:::'''Hongling:''' Those Cloud Knights in charge of security could not even catch up to me. When I got onto the stage, I hugged Master Yanqing tightly, and it took quite a while before they managed to separate us.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} The Cloud Knights did not lock you up?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502140107-->
