::{{DIcon|Talk}} What exactly do you like about Yanqing?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502140113-->
:::'''Hongling:''' Because he is the ideal that I've always aspired to become!
:::'''Hongling:''' Since young, I've dreamed of becoming an unparalleled swordmaster, eradicating abominations for the Xianzhou and accomplishing outstanding feats. However, due to my mediocre talent, my sword skills remained rudimentary, and I could not even pass the selection examination for the Cloud Knights...
:::'''Hongling:''' However, the appearance of Master Yanqing reignited the spark within me. Compared to someone mediocre like me, he's a genius of the sword, and I hope that my dreams can be realized through him.
:::'''Hongling:''' But watching Master Yanqing is like watching my dreams come to fruition. When I look at how hard he works, I feel like I've gained some strength too. Even without talent, I'll continue to pursue swordsmanship in hopes of one day becoming a swordmaster like Master Yanqing!
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
